<p>Coffee Timer was designed to help make gourmet coffee easily at home. It has preset timer and instructions for various brewing methods, such as French Press, Hario V60, and Chemex. Users can also add customized timers that fit better with their own brewing method. Timer sets include suggested amounts of coffee and water, total brew duration, and other useful brewing information.</p>

