<p>Some challenges I faced while designing were</p>
<ul>
  <li>Displaying the different stages of brewing in a seamless, progressive manner</li>
  <li>Showcasing both progression of time and visual location of the queues on the radial path (i.e. at 30' mark, bloom stage stops)</li>
  <li>Displaying descriptions for the different brewing stages</li>
  <li>Supporting pausing and how to strategically place the pause button</li>
</ul>

